    <updated>2015-12-25T04:18:28.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Raw, dry bamboo snow will suck up oil, grease or water from a floor in a moment.  A slippery floor can be made safe to walk on in seconds with a sprinkle of Bamboo Snow.</p>
<p>Sweep up the spill with a broom and dustpan. Could not be easier.</p>
]]></content>
